
### **package.json:**

This file is automatically created when you run `npm init`. Ensure it has the dependencies `express` and `mongoose`.

Example:

```json
{
  "name": "my-mongo-app",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A simple Node.js app using MongoDB",
  "main": "app.js",
  "scripts": {
    "start": "node app.js"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "express": "^4.17.1",
    "mongoose": "^6.0.14"
  },
  "author": "",
  "license": "ISC"
}
